elements.text:
1. Which 1995 Vinod Khanna movie shares its name with a 2004 comedy film in which his son played a pivotal role?

:x: Agnipath

:x: Taal

2. How do the protagonists of "The Burning Train" eventually stop the burning train?

:white_check_mark: By detaching the engine

:x: Emergency brakes
:x: Draining the fuel

:tada: Nice job! <@U03AHQURB98>

:x: Prasoon Joshi

:tada: Nice job! <@U02UUFWM4MV>

9. Which singer began her film career with a Sanskrit verse in the 1973 film "Abhimaan"?

:tada: Nice job! <@U03AHQURB98>
